Package: regin
Version: 0.2.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.35), systemd
Maintainer: exedev <exedev@driessel.exe.xyz>
Description: AI-powered monitoring and audit agent
 Named after the dwarf smith from the Sigurd saga.
 .
 Config-free: all settings stored in SQLite, managed via
 'regin config set/get/list'. Auto-starts daemon on first use.
 .
  - regind: user daemon (runs via systemd --user)
  - regin: CLI with chat, task execution, scheduling, config
 .
 Skills are markdown files: system skills in /usr/share/regin/skills/,
 user skills in ~/.config/regin/skills/ (user overrides system).
